<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">I’ve been unable to reach you since you were referred to us by&nbsp;</span></font><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">your friend&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>{!Lead.Referred_By_Account__c}</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.</span></font></span><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br></font><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>This means I’ve been unable to provide you with the business insurance quote you requested.<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>If you are&nbsp;</span><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">interested in proceeding with your quote</b><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">, reply with the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively you can give me a ring on&nbsp;</span><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">01242 808 740</b><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">.<br></font></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white;"><br></font><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}<br></font></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></font></span><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
